This is some add-on policies for Perl::Critic, for miscellaneous bugs,
compibility, efficiency and some cosmetic things.  See the POD of
Perl::Critic::Pulp for the full list.

The only major prerequisite is Perl::Critic itself, though
"PerlMinimumVersionAndWhy" does nothing without Perl::MinimumVersion.

The Perl-Critic-Pulp home page is

    http://user42.tuxfamily.org/perl-critic-pulp/index.html
